To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private T3MovingAverage _t3;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_t3 = T3(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_t3.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "t3movingaverage", _t3.Current.Value);
}
